I think you may have two projects referencing different versions of Newtonsoft. It&#39;s also possible you are using a library that requires a particular version of Newtonsoft, other than the one referenced by your project.

Inspect the references of every project in the solution and make sure that, if Newtonsoft is present, it points to the right version (v12.0.0.0). 

